    <briefdescription>
<para>Lock-free Single-Producer Single-Consumer (SPSC) queue. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides a lock-free, zero-allocation SPSC item queue designed for high-performance ISR-to-Task, Task-to-Task, or Inter-Core (multicore) message passing without spinlocks or disabling interrupts. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
